description.gco:CharacterString: The data for this layer was published with multiple feature classes, and the metadata was generated from the “WI_DATCP_LandWater_2017” feature dataset.

Imported the following feature classes to the feature dataset WI_DATCP_LandWater_2017: ATRAZINE_PA, ATRAZINE_PA_LWRV, CREP_LOC_2016, LIVESITE_CNTY_ORD, LIVESITE_CVT_ORD, STATEWIDE_AEA, STATEWIDE_FP_PLAN, STATEWIDE_FP_ZON, WI_DRAINAGE_DIST.
Created new feature dataset, WI_DATCP_LandWater_2017, within the geodatabase, DATCP_LAND_WATER_MGMT.
